
                         Search Add-On for Reposify

  What is it?
  -----------

  The Search Add-On for Reposify is a Splunk Search Add-On
  for interacting with the Reposify REST API https://api.reposify.com.
  Under the hood it uses the python-reposify Python library
  https://github.com/reposify/reposify-python.

  Installation
  ------------

  This app should be installed on a Splunk Search Head. There is a web-based
  setup screen where you should fill in your Reposify API token.

  Usage
  -----

  This command is a generating command, meaning it should be used at the start
  of your search, like so:

     o | reposify banner=welcome

  Currently, it supports only the Insights part of the Reposify API,
  and a "filters" or "banner" parameter must be supplied
  for a successful search. See https://docs.reposify.com for more
  information.

